                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/9628.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Constitutionalist Secretary for Foreign
                            Affairs</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nogales</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-11-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 6, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor to inform you of the appointment of Señor Roberto V. Pesqueira
                    as Confidential Agent of the Constitutionalist Government at Washington.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Francisco Escudero</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
